<div class="section3-about">
    <div class="section3-about__heading">
        <h1 class="section3-about__main">Avoiding Scams & Frauds</h1>
        <h2 class="section3-about__sub">Always deal locally, face-to-face</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="section3-about__groupcontent">
        <div class="section3-about__group">
            <div class="section3-about__body">
                <p class="section3-about__bodytext">When browsing craigslist, it is important that you are alert and aware to scammers and frauds and know what
                    course of action to take when spotting one. Safety and security of our customers is our number one priority
                    on craigslist and we are dedicated towards helping those facing situations involving scams and frauds. A
                    good rule of thumb when using craigslist is to deal locally and meet face-to-face to avoid scam attempts.
                    Here are some other important tips to remember when you suspect an offer on craigslist is a scam.</p>
            </div>
        
            <div class="section3-about__block">
                <div class="section3-about__text">
                    <p class="section3-about__sentence">To know more about scams and frauds and to see real examples, click here for more information.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="section3-about__button1">
                    <a class="section3-about__cta1" href="#">More Information</a>
                </div>
                <div class="section3-about__button2">
                    <a class="section3-about__cta2" href="#">More Info</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <div class="section3-about__list">
            <ul class="section3-about__points">
                <li class="section3-about__bullets1">Do not provide payment to anyone you have not met in person</li>
                <li class="section3-about__bullets2">Beware offers involving shipping</li>
                <li class="section3-about__bullets3">Never wire funds (e.g. Western Union)</li>
                <li class="section3-about__bullets4">Don’t accept cashier/certified checks or money orders</li>
                <li class="section3-about__bullets5">Transactions are between users only</li>
                <li class="section3-about__bullets6">Never give out financial information</li>
                <li class="section3-about__bullets7">Do not rent or purchase sight-unseen</li>
                <li class="section3-about__bullets8">Refuse background/credit checks</li>
                <li class="section3-about__bullets9">Do not interact with “craigslist voicemails,” no such service exists</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>